      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/led_zeppelin_led_zeppelin5881711201488186.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;border-right-width: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px&#34; title=&#34;led_zeppelin_led_zeppelin-588171-1201488186&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/led_zeppelin_led_zeppelin5881711201488186_thumb.jpg&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;led_zeppelin_led_zeppelin-588171-1201488186&#34; width=&#34;604&#34; height=&#34;242&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;昨天无意中又听到led zeppelin 的 stairway to heaven.8分钟长的歌一口气播放三遍，那种感觉好像心里有话要说，却在后面强劲的吉他solo中被封住了口，跟着飘忽不 定的吉他飘了起来，直至灵魂出鞘&lt;/p&gt;</description>
